column5: Has anybody heard if the Trillium Motel has survived the last couple years?? Can't seem to get a response by telephone. Thanks, Jay
Stayed there last sept,try to send them an email,keep trying I'm sure there still open.

The wife finally made contact with the Trillium Motel after trying many times many different ways.They are in the process of opening up with shortened hours and did set us up with a reservation in July. They have been ill this winter and were shut down. Later, Jay
